break-word;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span></span></span>\r\n													</p>\r\n													<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;text-indent:17.95pt;line-height:18px;\">\r\n														<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">消癌平糖浆的优势：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">一、服用更加方便，吸收更为充分，尤其适合晚期肿瘤病人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">二、诱导肿瘤细胞发生细胞周期阻滞，抑制肿瘤细胞分裂增殖，促使其分化，阻碍肿瘤生长，可使瘤体缩小或消失。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">三、增加<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">CD4+/CD8+</span>比值，刺激网状内皮细胞增生，增强吞噬细胞活力，提高免疫系统功能。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">四、通过癌细胞内信号传导系统，选择性抑制<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">Na+&nbsp;.K+.ATP</span>酶活性，下调癌基因表达，诱导肿瘤细胞凋亡。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">五、控制原法灶的转移及转移灶的继续扩散，明显缓解临床症状，提高生存质量。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">六、保护骨髓造血功能，增加白细胞数量，降低放化疗及癌性毒素对造血系统的损伤，与化疗、放疗合用有明显的减毒增效作用，尤其适用于无法手术、对放化疗毒副作用无法耐受的肿瘤患者。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">七、改善机体代谢，保护心肝肾功能。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【成<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>　份】乌骨藤</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【药理作用】乌骨藤独有成分具有诱导和促使微管（肿瘤细胞赖以分裂、扩散的载体）蛋白聚合、微管装配与微管稳定的独特作用机制，从而抑制肿瘤细胞的有丝分裂，达到抑癌、治癌的目的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【性　<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>状】本品为棕褐色的粘稠液体；味甜、苦。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【功能主治】</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">用于<a href=\"http://www.zlxty.com/zlzt.asp\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;color:#FF0000;text-decoration:none;\">食道癌、胃癌、肺癌、肝癌</a>。对<a href=\"http://www.zlxty.com/zlzt.asp\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;color:#FF0000;text-decoration:none;\">恶性淋巴</a>癌、对大肠癌、宫颈癌、白血病等恶性肿瘤亦有疗效。并可配合放疗、化疗和手术后治疗。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【用法用量】口服，一次<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">10-&nbsp;20ml&nbsp;</span>，一日<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">&nbsp;3&nbsp;</span>次。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【禁<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>忌】孕妇忌服。</span></span>\r\n													</p>\r\n												</div>\r\n											</td>\r\n										</tr>\r\n									</tbody>\r\n								</table>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>','消癌平糖浆','长春英联生物','10ml*10支','盒','国药准字Z20053670','YPBH894')
