d-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span></span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:18px;text-indent:25.9pt;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【规　格】每支</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">10ml<o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:18px;text-indent:25.9pt;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">【贮　藏】密封，避光，置阴凉干燥处。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span></span>\r\n									</p>\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:18px;text-indent:25.9pt;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【包　装】玻璃管制口服液瓶装，</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">10ml×6</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">支；</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">&nbsp;10ml×10</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"word-wrap