\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span></span>\r\n													</p>\r\n													<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;text-indent:25.9pt;line-height:18px;\">\r\n														<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">性状</span></span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">：本品为肠溶胶囊剂，内容物为淡黄色粉末；气微香，味苦。</span></span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span></span>\r\n													</p>\r\n													<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;text-indent:25.9pt;line-height:18px;\">\r\n														<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">功能主治：解毒，消肿，止痛。用于中晚期肿瘤，慢性乙型肝炎等症有明显疗效。</span></span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span></span>\r\n													</p>\r\n													<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;text-indent:25.9pt;line-height:18px;\">\r\n														<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">用法用量：口服。一次</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">2</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font