le=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">等，以及止痛、止血、控制感染、腹水等措施。西黄丸组：加服西黄丸，用法：每次</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">3g</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">，每日</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">次，</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">10</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">日为</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">1</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">个疗程，服用</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">2</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">个疗程以上。</span></span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span></span>\r\n													</p>\r\n													<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:18px;text-indent:1cm;\">\r\n														<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word