-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span>\r\n													</p>\r\n													<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:18px;text-indent:28.25pt;\">\r\n														<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【主要成份】体外培育牛黄，麝香，乳香（醋制），没药（醋制）。</span></span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span></span>\r\n													</p>\r\n													<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;line-height:18px;text-indent:28.25pt;\">\r\n														<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【性</span></span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">状】本品为褐色的糊丸</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">气芳香</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\">,</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">味微苦。</span></span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><o:p style=\"wo