p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;text-indent:28.25pt;line-height:18px;\">\r\n														<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【批准文号】陕食药监健用字<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">06130297</span>号<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"><o:p style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\"></o:p></span></span></span>\r\n													</p>\r\n													<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;text-indent:28.25pt;line-height:18px;\">\r\n														<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【生产单位】咸阳滋润堂医药科技有限公司</span></span>\r\n													</p>\r\n												</div>\r\n											</td>\r\n										</tr>\r\n									</tbody>\r\n								</table>\r\n							</td>\r\n						</tr>\r\n					</tbody>\r\n				</table>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>','斑蝥瘤痛消','陕西滋润堂药业','100mm×123mm×4贴+消杀霜5g','盒','陕食药监健用字06130297号','YPBH940')
INSERT INTO `dy_product_field` VALUES('46','<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;empty-cells:show;font-family:Simsun;font-weight:bold;line-height:25px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#000000;font-size:12px;text-align:center;\" class=\"ke-zeroborder\">\r\n	<tbody style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">\r\n		<tr style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">\r\n			<td height=\"30\" align=\"left\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">\r\n				<span class=\"STYLE36\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">用药说明</span>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">\r\n			<td style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">\r\n				<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;empty-cells:show;\" class=\"ke-zeroborder\">\r\n					<tbody style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">\r\n						<tr style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">\r\n							<td width=\"20\" height=\"183\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">\r\n								&nbsp;\r\n							</td>\r\n							<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;line-height:24px;\">\r\n								<div id=\"intro\">\r\n									<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;text-indent:23.5pt;line-height:18px;\">\r\n										<span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\"><a href=\"http://www.zlxty.com/ypjs.asp?id=948\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;color:#FF0000;text-decoration:none;\">金水鲜胶囊</a>依据传统中医扶正荡邪理论，以鲜蛤蚧、鲜金钱白花蛇、鲜守宫、鲜西洋参、冬虫夏草入药，一改中药传统的炮制方法，采用超低温现代生化分离提取技术，将低温、快速、高效三者结合以最快速度将细胞内浆液中的活性物质仅以</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">2%</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">的比例提纯，最大限度地保持了鲜动植物的药物有效成份及其有效成份的分子结构的天然配比。实验证明，金水鲜胶囊的有效成份能够促进癌细胞膜的通透性，再加上其有效成份均为小分子物质，所以，它就克服传统抗癌药物无法突破癌细胞表面的胶原层，不易被人体吸收，无法直达要害的痼疾，顺利完成杀灭癌细胞的任务。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">　　金水鲜胶囊是天然基因类药物，多成份、多环节、多靶点的对肿瘤进行治疗，结合基因修复、基因识别、阻滞血管生成、微循环排斥、细胞静电吸附、阻断神经传导、减毒增效七大作用，能够（</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">1</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">）修复癌细胞</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">P21</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">小蛋白分子，恢复对癌细胞的调控，使癌细胞转化为正常细胞。（</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">2</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">）在人体内准确识别癌细胞与正常细胞，在对癌细胞实施精确打击的同时，还能加速正常细胞的生长和代谢速度，产生多种蛋白质，全面改善体内环境，消胸水、腹水，降低癌症并发症的发病率。（</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">3</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">）抑制癌细胞周围新生血管的生成，切断癌细胞的营养源，降低癌细胞生长速度。（</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">4</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">）改善微循环，使血管壁光滑，降低癌细胞的着床率，防止复发。（</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">5</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">）降解癌细胞膜的酸化环境，引起癌细胞表面负电荷降低，增加静电吸附作用，使原有癌细胞紧紧粘附在原发病灶上，无法脱离原发病灶而发生转移。（</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">6</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">）作用于中枢神经系统，阻断痛觉神经传导，消除癌痛。（</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">7</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">）提供多种营养物质，保护消化及造血系统不受伤害，提高骨髓细胞及白介素的数量，对放化疗有减毒增效作用。首次实现了对癌症的整合治疗，开创中药抗癌整合疗法之先河。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">　　</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">2000</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">年</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">10</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">月至</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">2002</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">年</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">8</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">月，由中国中医药大学牵头，会同中国中医研究院广安门医院、中国医学科学院肿瘤医院及北京中日友好医院等对</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">6356</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">例中、晚期癌症患者进行了长期的临床观察，结果表明：</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">“</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">金水鲜</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">”</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">对肺癌、食管癌、胃癌、肝癌、肠癌、胆囊癌、胰腺癌、乳腺癌、甲状腺癌、鼻咽癌、口腔癌、脑癌、淋巴癌、骨癌、白血病等恶性肿瘤具有广泛的治疗作用和显著的效果。受试者每天服用</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">“</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">金水鲜胶囊</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">”6</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">粒（每日三次，每次</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">2</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">粒），</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">2—4</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">周后，多数癌痛可以得到很好的控制；受试者的食欲、睡眠、精神、体力普遍好转，一部分卧床不起的病人甚至可以下地行走；胸水、腹水、癌热、食道梗阻等症状迅速缓解或消失；恶心呕吐、腹泻、溃疡、脱发等放化疗的毒副反应明显减轻。连续服用</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">7—16</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">周，白细胞恢复正常值，肿瘤的转移和扩散得到有效控制，总转移率降低</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">58.3% —66.7%</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">；肿瘤开始持续缩小</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">,</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">总有效率为</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">84.7%</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">，这说明</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">“</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">金水鲜胶囊</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">”</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">对中晚期癌症具有突出的疗效。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">金水鲜在癌症治疗中的突破</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">金水鲜胶囊是中国癌症研究基金会北京鲜药研制中心与清华大学生命科学与工程研究院共同研制的鲜动植物药剂，它以鲜动植物为组方，采用超低温</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">(<st1:chmetcnv tcsc=\"0\" numbertype=\"1\" negative=\"True\" hasspace=\"False\" sourcevalue=\"195\" unitname=\"℃\" w:st=\"on\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\">-195℃</st1:chmetcnv>)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">冷冻加工及先进的冻融技术，提取鲜蛤蚧、鲜金钱白花蛇、冬虫夏草、鲜西洋参等药品中的高效</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">抗癌生物活性物质入药，临床应用于中晚期癌症的治疗，对缩小肿块、消除癌痛、消除腹水、消除胸水总有效率达</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">88</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">．</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">4</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">％，这是来之不易的，是经过了大量的实验和临床研究以及一系列科学依法程序的严格审查才获得的。金水鲜对癌症的治疗突出体现在以下几个方面。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">一、金水鲜胶囊主治中晚期癌症，缩小肿块、消癌痛、消腹水、消胸水。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">金水鲜胶囊药物中的小分子活性成份可以增强癌细胞细胞膜的通透性。大量小分子活性物质进入癌细胞核内直接杀死癌细胞。阻断癌细胞</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">DNA</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">的复制，抑制癌细胞的生长。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">利用鸡胚</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">CAM</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">模型观察对血管新生的抑制作用结果表示：能抑制癌组织和血管生成和破坏病灶周围和内部已生成的血管网，这一作用可以使癌组织不能生长和坏死。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(3)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">小分子活性物质在机体内多途径、多方位、多环节、多靶位作用于癌细胞，使失控的癌细胞增殖和细胞分化得以逆转和控制，同时改进机体的不良状态，扶正荡邪。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(4)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">金水鲜胶囊中的小分子物质能作用于人体的中枢神经系统，切断痛觉神经的传导，作用于人体正常细胞，增强正常细胞的活性和代谢速度，可起到消癌痛、消胸水、消腹水作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(5)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">延长晚期癌症患者存活期，能抑制微小转移灶的血管生成，阻止恶性肿瘤进一步发展，控制肿瘤血管生成的微生态，微环境、微系统变化，延长患者生命。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">二、金水鲜胶囊有效阻止早期癌症的转移。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">早期癌症治愈的关键是阻止复发和转移，试验发现肿瘤的增殖和转移扩散，依赖于瘤体血管的生成，金水鲜含有抑制血管生成的成份，能抑制癌细胞新血管的形成，阻断病灶周围血管网的形成，使癌组织不能生长，阻止转移。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">降解癌细胞膜的酸化环境，引起癌细胞表面负电荷降低，由于静电吸附作用，使原有癌细胞紧紧粘附在原发病灶上，无法脱离原发病灶而发生转移。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(3)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">可以改变癌细胞表面的离子状态，影响和降低癌细胞的游走与浸润。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">三、减轻手术、放、化疗中的毒副反应。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">经中国中医研究院等科研部门进行的药效学研究证实：</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(1)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">免疫学</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">(</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">扶正</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">研究：分别从整体水平</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">(DTH</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">、抗体分泌细胞</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">、细胞水平</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">(T</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">、</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">B</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">细胞增殖</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">及分子水平</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">(TNF)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">研究表明，可明显增强正常机体及荷瘤动物的免疫功能。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(2)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">抑瘤</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">(</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">荡邪</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">研究对</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">W256</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">、</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">S180</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">、</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">H22</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">均有明显的抑制癌细胞生长的作用。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (3)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">减毒研究，可减轻化疗药物对肝脏及造血系统的毒性反应，可与放、化疗合用，有助于减轻放、化疗的毒副反应，使白细胞血小板不致下降，减轻恶心、呕吐和食欲不振等消化道症状，提高放、化疗疗效。该药合并环磷酰胺，能明显提高荷瘤小鼠骨髓有核细胞数，可明显减低化疗对骨髓细胞的损害。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(4)</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">促进手术后伤口快速愈合，防止伤口感染，恢复体力。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">金水鲜胶囊在肿瘤治疗领域显示了广阔的前景，中日友好医院肿瘤科主任张代钊教授经临床后在报告里写到</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">“</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">目前没有几个药品能与金水鲜胶囊相比</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">”</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">。中国癌症研究基金会理事长李保荣教授说：</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">“</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">我们要给以金水胶囊为代表的鲜药制剂定一个位置，我们</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">搞了一个祖国自己的抗癌药，是不容易的，我们要珍惜它、爱护它、推广它，让它为癌症康复做贡献</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">”</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n<br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">【药品名称】</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">品</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><span style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;\">名：金水鲜胶囊</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"word-wrap:break-word;font-size:10.5pt;line-height:21px;font-family:Arial;letter-spacing:0.4pt;\"><br style=\"word-wrap:break-word;\" />\r\n</span><span style=\"word-wrap:break-wo